casebody.data:
Moellering et al.; Top Design of Cincinnati, Inc. et al., Appellees, v. City of Cincinnati et al.; Schweitzer Construction Company, Appellant.

[Cite as Moellering v. Cincinnati (1988), 40 Ohio St. 3d 20.]

(No. 87-1883 Submitted October 19, 1988 Decided November 30, 1988.) Benesch, Friedlander, Coplan & Aronoff, Timothy L. Bouscaren and Ronald L. House, for appellees. Bloom & Greene Co., L.P.A., and Lawrence A. Flemer, for appellant.

Because there was no final appealable order before the court of appeals, the judgment of the court of appeals is reversed and the cause is remanded to the trial court. In re Trust of Hall (1987), 34 Ohio St. 3d 47, 517 N.E. 2d 536.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
